<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 20:07:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡没有告诉拜登有关以色列人和加沙战争的全部真相</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-tell-biden-the-whole-truth-about-israelis-and-the-gaza-war/0000018e-389b-dc74-adbe-bcbf118b0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡告诉拜登和 AIPAC，以色列人绝大多数支持他的战时政策，而忽略了公众对他的领导力和加沙“全面胜利”承诺的信心下降。问题是以色列人何时以及是否会开始呼吁结束战争</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 19:41:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-didnt-tell-biden-the-whole-truth-about-israelis-and-the-gaza-war/0000018e-389b-dc74-adbe-bcbf118b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军最高指挥官在呼吁以色列领导人“无愧于他们的士兵”后接受质询</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-officer-to-be-questioned-after-calls-for-leaders-to-be-worthy-of-their-soldiers/0000018e-390b-d2fd-a1fe-3dfbe9980000</link><description>双桅船。丹·戈德福斯将军呼吁以色列领导人“无愧于预备役军人，他们不关心自己来自哪一方，并肩作战”，并“确保每个人都参与其中”，但这一呼吁并未得到他的上级指挥官的批准。他向加沙地带以外的媒体发表的声明</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 19:40:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/top-idf-officer-to-be-questioned-after-calls-for-leaders-to-be-worthy-of-their-soldiers/0000018e-390b-d2fd-a1fe-3dfbe9980000</guid></item><item><title>戏剧性的转变，以色列表示打算向加沙“淹没”人道主义援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-changes-its-policy-on-supplies-to-gaza-intends-to-flood-in-aid-idf-says/0000018e-390e-db12-a9ef-fbff14c50000</link><description>这一决定是在国际社会向内塔尼亚胡政府施加巨大压力之后做出的，包括在华盛顿和伦敦对来访的部长本尼·甘茨提出严厉警告，甘茨被告知以色列需要采取更多措施来缓解加沙地带的饥饿</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 18:42:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-changes-its-policy-on-supplies-to-gaza-intends-to-flood-in-aid-idf-says/0000018e-390e-db12-a9ef-fbff14c50000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 159 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-159/0000018e-38e1-d21d-a3ef-3be787fe0000</link><description>南非表示，持有南非公民身份的以色列国防军士兵在进入该国时将被逮捕 ■ 在与拜登之间前所未有的紧张局势中，内塔尼亚胡预计将在参议院共和党撤退问题上发表讲话 ■ 近东救济工程处：据报道，以色列袭击拉法食品配送中心后，至少一名工作人员被杀 ■ 这是自以来的首次10 月 7 日，运载援助物资的卡车直接从以色列进入加沙北部 ■ 战争开始 159 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 17:39:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-159/0000018e-38e1-d21d-a3ef-3be787fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列一直将约旦河西岸与加沙地带分开。战争期间就等于死刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-been-separating-the-west-bank-from-gaza-during-war-it-becomes-a-death-sentence/0000018e-3874-d2fd-a1fe-3df58c940000</link><description>自上世纪90年代以来，以色列一直致力于将巴勒斯坦领土分为两部分。事实上，加沙人暂时流离失所到西岸并未被考虑，这表明以色列造成的分裂是多么根深蒂固。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 17:23:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-has-been-separating-the-west-bank-from-gaza-during-war-it-becomes-a-death-sentence/0000018e-3874-d2fd-a1fe-3df58c940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会批准以色列修订后的2024年预算，为加沙战争提供资金，解决联盟争端</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/knesset-approves-israels-amended-2024-budget-to-fund-gaza-war-amid-coalition-dispute/0000018e-3863-dda5-a9ff-fdefb3cc0000</link><description>在与战争无关的支出问题上出现政治争端和分歧后，2024 年修订预算法以 62 名支持者对 55 名反对者的多数票获得通过</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 16:22:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/knesset-approves-israels-amended-2024-budget-to-fund-gaza-war-amid-coalition-dispute/0000018e-3863-dda5-a9ff-fdefb3cc0000</guid></item><item><title>与甘茨分手后，萨尔可能获得战时内阁席位——但内塔尼亚胡担心本-格维尔的要求也会随之而来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/saar-could-get-a-war-cabinet-seat-but-netanyahu-fears-ben-gvirs-demands-will-follow/0000018e-3801-d21d-a3ef-3b4721070000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡并不急于屈服于萨尔的要求，而甘茨的人民坚持认为战时内阁中唯一的空闲席位是为亚伊尔·拉皮德保留的</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 15:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/saar-could-get-a-war-cabinet-seat-but-netanyahu-fears-ben-gvirs-demands-will-follow/0000018e-3801-d21d-a3ef-3b4721070000</guid></item><item><title>病毒式斋月广告聚焦以色列加沙战争中的巴勒斯坦儿童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/the-viral-ramadan-commercial-spotlighting-palestinian-children-amid-israels-war-in-gaza/0000018e-3389-d9f7-a5ee-f7cbd44a0000</link><description>科威特电信巨头 Zain 今年发布的这段视频突显了加沙灾难性的人道主义局势，以 10 岁难民汉达拉的标志性巴勒斯坦漫画为特色，传达了坚持和回归的信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:49:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/the-viral-ramadan-commercial-spotlighting-palestinian-children-amid-israels-war-in-gaza/0000018e-3389-d9f7-a5ee-f7cbd44a0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯、萨达姆和普京的朋友乔治·加洛韦是英国政治的未来吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/is-george-galloway-friend-of-hamas-saddam-and-putin-the-future-of-british-politics/0000018e-37dd-d2aa-a5ae-f7fdd0290000</link><description>乔治·加洛韦是表演政治的孔雀，现在正处于极左转变为极右的特殊政治暮色中。但他最近在英国选举中取得的成功，被称为“对加沙的公投”和“工人而不是工人”的公投，将进一步推动整个政治领域将战争工具化的热潮</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:24:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-opinion/.premium/is-george-galloway-friend-of-hamas-saddam-and-putin-the-future-of-british-politics/0000018e-37dd-d2aa-a5ae-f7fdd0290000</guid></item><item><title>富兰克林·福尔：“美国犹太人的日常生活将被反犹太主义打断”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-13/ty-article-podcast/franklin-foer-everyday-jewish-u-s-life-will-be-punctuated-by-antisemitism/0000018e-3535-da0e-a78f-fd3d5cd90000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 13:03:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-13/ty-article-podcast/franklin-foer-everyday-jewish-u-s-life-will-be-punctuated-by-antisemitism/0000018e-3535-da0e-a78f-fd3d5cd90000</guid></item><item><title>抛弃甘茨后，萨尔并没有给内塔尼亚胡提供救生索。他递给他一个氧气瓶</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/by-leaving-gantz-saar-didnt-give-netanyahu-breathing-room-he-gave-him-an-oxygen-tank/0000018e-372c-d8f9-a98e-7fefdb5d0000</link><description>吉迪恩·萨尔令人费解地退出甘茨的民族团结党，使内塔尼亚胡政府内部反对派的一名关键人物被除名，为总理赢得了宝贵的时间，并可能进一步推迟选举</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:47:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/by-leaving-gantz-saar-didnt-give-netanyahu-breathing-room-he-gave-him-an-oxygen-tank/0000018e-372c-d8f9-a98e-7fefdb5d0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷附近发生刺伤袭击，两名以色列人受轻伤，嫌疑人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/two-israelis-lightly-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-near-jerusalem-suspect-killed/0000018e-3799-d977-a5ae-7fdd25460000</link><description>17 岁的嫌疑人接近检查站并试图刺伤保安人员，造成一名 25 岁的平民保安人员和一名 19 岁的士兵受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:24:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/two-israelis-lightly-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-near-jerusalem-suspect-killed/0000018e-3799-d977-a5ae-7fdd25460000</guid></item><item><title>外交部长称南非将逮捕持有双重国籍的以色列士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-to-arrest-israeli-soldiers-holding-dual-citizenship-foreign-minister-says/0000018e-36e3-d0ac-a1cf-3ef7f8650000</link><description>该国外交部长表示，持有以色列和南非双重国籍的以色列国防军士兵将被立即逮捕。以色列军队正在为其他可能效仿的军队做准备</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:42:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-to-arrest-israeli-soldiers-holding-dual-citizenship-foreign-minister-says/0000018e-36e3-d0ac-a1cf-3ef7f8650000</guid></item><item><title>本格维尔支持枪杀 13 岁巴勒斯坦儿童的警察后，以色列总检察长发出警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-warns-ben-gvir-for-backing-cop-who-killed-13-year-old-palestinian/0000018e-3774-d361-a3de-7775b32a0000</link><description>本-格维尔出现在正在接受调查的警察局，称“英雄”做得堪称典范；总检察长加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉：任何干扰案件调查的行为都是非法的</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:22:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-warns-ben-gvir-for-backing-cop-who-killed-13-year-old-palestinian/0000018e-3774-d361-a3de-7775b32a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国对以色列实施武器禁运真的能阻止加沙战争吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/would-a-u-s-arms-embargo-on-israel-really-stop-the-war-in-gaza/0000018e-36c2-d8f9-a98e-7ec381950000</link><description>尽管美国政府可以利用一些公共和私人手段来表达对以色列军事行动的不满，但这些手段都不像一些人所说的那么容易。人们担心，孤立可能会进一步加剧以色列和内塔尼亚胡的胆量，并可能给总理带来国内胜利</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:11:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/would-a-u-s-arms-embargo-on-israel-really-stop-the-war-in-gaza/0000018e-36c2-d8f9-a98e-7ec381950000</guid></item><item><title>以色列加大与真主党高风险敌对行动的赌注</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-ups-the-ante-in-high-risk-hostilities-with-hezbollah/0000018e-3447-da0e-a78f-fc7ff5510000</link><description>以色列国防军进攻行动扩大到黎巴嫩贝卡谷地 — — 以及真主党的强化反应 — — 使双方更接近一场他们试图避免的战争</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 04:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-ups-the-ante-in-high-risk-hostilities-with-hezbollah/0000018e-3447-da0e-a78f-fc7ff5510000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙，以色列国防部长加兰特暗示拉法行动；以色列国防军空袭黎巴嫩哈马斯官员身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-live/aid-trucks-enter-northern-gaza-from-israel-for-first-time-since-war-on-hamas-broke-out/0000018e-35a6-d9f7-a5ee-f7efeae50000</link><description>哈马斯呼吁西岸巴勒斯坦人向圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺进军，与以色列安全部队对峙 ■ 17 岁巴勒斯坦人在西岸检查站持刀刺伤两名以色列人后身亡 ■ 两名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸检查站被以色列国防军炮火打死约旦河西岸城市杰宁和吉瓦特泽耶夫定居点附近的另外两个城市 ■ 德国批准武装部队向加沙空投援助物资</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 02:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article-live/aid-trucks-enter-northern-gaza-from-israel-for-first-time-since-war-on-hamas-broke-out/0000018e-35a6-d9f7-a5ee-f7efeae50000</guid></item><item><title>西岸警察局长：大多数关于定居者暴力的投诉都是虚假的，由无政府主义者提出</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-police-chief-most-complaints-of-settler-violence-are-false-filed-by-anarchists/0000018e-34cf-d5ad-addf-7cdff2310000</link><description>议会小组委员会周二召开会议，讨论“活动人士的煽动活动”。地区警察指挥官指责人权组织“声誉受损”</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 23:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-police-chief-most-complaints-of-settler-violence-are-false-filed-by-anarchists/0000018e-34cf-d5ad-addf-7cdff2310000</guid></item><item><title>“不可逆转的损害”：以色列火山研究所负责人抗议预算削减计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/irreversible-damage-heads-of-israels-volcani-institute-protest-planned-budget-cuts/0000018e-342c-d5ad-addf-7c3d53b50000</link><description>火山研究所代理所长什穆埃尔·阿苏林 (Shmuel Assouline) 表示，由于提议的削减，该机构已暂停其活动，他警告说，这将导致该研究所关闭、诉讼和损害、正在申请的专利被取消以及其所拥有的知识产权的损失。国家</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 21:24:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/irreversible-damage-heads-of-israels-volcani-institute-protest-planned-budget-cuts/0000018e-342c-d5ad-addf-7c3d53b50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方在东耶路撒冷射杀一名向他们发射烟花的 13 岁青少年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-fatally-shot-a-13-year-old-who-launched-fireworks-at-them-in-east-jerusalem/0000018e-3457-da0e-a78f-fc7f43e80000</link><description>据难民营一名居民称，烟花并非针对军官，也不会对他们构成威胁。国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔在回应这一事件时表示，他向警察对事件的处理“致敬”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 20:35:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-fatally-shot-a-13-year-old-who-launched-fireworks-at-them-in-east-jerusalem/0000018e-3457-da0e-a78f-fc7f43e80000</guid></item></channel></rss>